Attribute Name: TOTAL_API_QUOTE

Related CTE(s):
FQ_BASE, ALL_APPS, IHQ_COMB, IHQ_SAMP1, BASE_SUM1

Source Fields Used:
- AGGREGATOR_INDICATOR
- QUOTE_STATUS_CODE
- APPLICATION_IDENTIFIER

Technical Transformation Summary:
Calculated as a count of records where AGGREGATOR_INDICATOR = 'Y', representing records originating from aggregator channels. Aggregation is performed in BASE_SUM1.

Business Logic:
Represents the total number of eligibility quote records generated via aggregator channels. These correspond to the initial stage of the customer journey before progressing to further eligibility checks or full applications.

Journey Stage:
Stage 1 – API / Aggregator Quote (First Check)

Assumptions / Open Questions:
- Confirm whether this metric includes only quote-level records (QUOTE_STATUS_CODE = 'Q') or also includes full application records ('F').
- Confirm the grain of counting (quote-level vs application-level).
- Validate alignment with the "Aggregator Quote to Conversion" metric in the dashboard.